Class LLVMParser

java.lang.Object
LLVMParser
public class LLVMParser extends Object
This class is responsible for generating the LLVM code from the parse tree.

      public String[] generate(ParseTree parseTree) throws RuntimeException
      Generates LLVM code from the provided parse tree.
      Parameters:
      parseTree - The parse tree to generate the LLVM code from.
      Returns:
      An array containing the name of the program and the generated LLVM code.
      Throws:
      RuntimeException - If an unknown non-terminal expression is found.
